benchmarkInfo.name: Long Text Collaboration
benchmarkInfo.userA: This is a longer text that simulates real document editing. It contains multiple sentences and should test the system's ability to handle continuous input from multiple users.
benchmarkInfo.userB: Meanwhile, another user is also editing the same document. This creates a realistic collaborative editing scenario where multiple people work on the same content simultaneously.
benchmarkInfo.description: Continuous long-text input; tests sustained performance and stability.
